  "id": "2666956830_2",
  "title": "公安部通报：陈某编造“工行假金条”，被依法追责",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   7月2日，公安部公布涉民生等领域网络谣言8起典型案例，\n   <strong>\n    其中包括此前备受关注的“工行两售出金条发现疑似杂质”一事。\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   案例称，陈某编造传播“在工商银行购买的金条剪开发现杂质”网络谣言案。近日，上海公安网安部门查明，陈某（男，46岁）为博取关注、吸粉引流，在某短视频平台发布内容为“工行假金条，官方发通告！假作真时真亦假，无为有处有还无！”的谣言信息，\n   <strong>\n    误导大量网民关注和讨论，对相关单位正常经营产生影响。\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"519473178\" data-ratio=\"0.5099206349206349\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"504\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SicLFic2cPia2LEKzThQzyJy953ftDawGUsH5WK7yGJR4mSWaGO9syB2ly1eG2ky8cCHdEicCEQwlpOWQ/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: MicrosoftYaHei;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(248, 249, 249);width: 1080px !important;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\"/>\n  <span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;'>\n   资料图\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style='font-family: mp-quote, \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;'>\n   通报称，8起典型案例涉案人员均已被依法追究相应法律责任。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   今年5月，网传一客户在该工行购买金条发现疑似杂质。中国工商银行上海市嘉定支行后回应称，经核实，该情况不属实，并附上情况说明和检测报告。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FxrFYciaHL08Au5yvNxx1mSh6OPxzqbt3ZpCO5h2icQSWHprZMJh5xdG4WFClNAOhjTm9ZswqvNYavdwR5Hc4cNPw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4058436941509820422\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4058436941509820422\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-w=\"1080\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border-radius: 4px;\">\n  </iframe>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   工行上海嘉定支行当时表示，经上海市计量测试技术研究院国家金银制品质量检验检测中心（上海）检测，两款金条检测报告均记载“检测结论：金含量为99.99%”，无质量问题。\n   <strong>\n    经上述质检机构以专业方式清洗，疑似杂质已脱落，应为金条售出后的外部附着物。以上结论均获客户认可。\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <strong>\n    <br/>\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <hr style='max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-style: solid;border-right-width: 0px;border-bottom-width: 0px;border-left-width: 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.098);transform-origin: 0px 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'/>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   来源：澎湃新闻，记者：胡志挺\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   本期编辑：刘杰、方梓祎\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-wo